::Battera::

She looked at the two bots. This was getting confusing.
"Who is Optimus Prime? Are you this bot? And if your the leader, Why 
hasn't anyone mentioned you before?"
She was starting to get nervous again.  This was higly unusual and 
she didn't know who to trust or what to think on this matter.
